"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab2bbf43f2b817b6230779c969280dd60a61cd2","tid":1219712,"uid":90025,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:45:17.000Z","msg":"得啦 俾你講咗"},{"pid":"d73ec339b6a24e5835838e4fbe24104dd98f679a","tid":1219712,"uid":148987,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:46:55.000Z","msg":"「黃絲督察」被裁定一項藏有271份兒童色情物品罪成候判<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社會新聞<br />\n<br />\n撰文：梁芷君<br />\n2017-11-27 13:09<br />\n最後更新日期：2017-11-27 13:09<br />\n<br />\n被喻為「黃絲督察」施恒，於2014年佔領行動期間，利用警隊電腦系統，取得同袍個人資料後於網上社交平台發布，而被警方調查後，期間更發現他的電腦及外置硬碟藏有逾270 段兒童色情影片。他早前已承認一項不誠實取用電腦罪，今再被裁定一項管有兒童色情物品罪名，還押至至12月11日判刑，以待索閱心理及精神報告。施得悉裁決後，拭淚及啜泣，有公眾人士大叫「撐住呀施sir」。"},{"pid":"bcf8855720871ab075d212b45f5fdac06ece2304","tid":1219712,"uid":148987,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:47:18.000Z","msg":"此post好快完"},{"pid":"28ecb3f95b1a5f0691ca8c85dacb7c171661ac4a","tid":1219712,"uid":15538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:48:08.000Z","msg":"負評嗰個，出聲解釋吓"},{"pid":"2af383fc5af02b1ab4b467a15290902f8ddcf3cd","tid":1219712,"uid":56702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:49:29.000Z","msg":"徐步高前往中國大陸消遣時，在羅湖關卡高呼「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>平反六四、打倒共產黨</strong></span>」的口號"},{"pid":"1333c7b1a5affbda3c21465d45b1cf79eae39e53","tid":1219712,"uid":15538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bcf8855720871ab075d212b45f5fdac06ece2304","tid":1219712,"uid":148987,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:47:18.000Z","msg":"此post好快完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:49:59.000Z","msg":"係我唔好 一嚟就出boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n無計，黑警多如牛毛，義警萬中無一"},{"pid":"12e8e84586db61e2898cf58982aba6d0983e00d4","tid":1219712,"uid":52474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"徐sir當年走得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /